      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>Step 7</strong></p>
        <p>文档</p>
  - elementId: p10-detail-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [60, 215, 400, 32]
    content:
      style: "$subheading"
      fontSize: 20
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>关键步骤说明</strong></p>
  - elementId: p10-detail-left-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [60, 260, 560, 380]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$cardBg"
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 1
      color: "$border"
  - elementId: p10-detail-left-text
    elementType: text
    bounds: [80, 275, 520, 350]
    content:
      style: "$body"
      fontSize: 15
      lineHeight: 1.6
      align: [left, top]
      text: |
        <p><strong style="color:$primary;">Step 1 需求分析</strong></p>
        <p>读取 docs/requirements/ 对应需求；如不存在，拒绝实现并要求先补充需求</p>
        <p style="margin-top:8px"><strong style="color:$primary;">Step 2 识别 Builder</strong></p>
        <p>新增 Entity → 创建 {Entity}Builder；复用已有 Builder → 检查 src/test/support/builder/</p>
        <p style="margin-top:8px"><strong style="color:$primary;">Step 3 编写失败测试（红）</strong></p>
        <p>单元测试：Service 层（Mockito）；集成测试：Controller 层（MockMvc + H2）</p>
        <p style="margin-top:8px"><strong style="color:$primary;">Step 4 最小实现（绿）</strong></p>
        <p>Controller → Service → Repository 分层实现</p>
  - elementId: p10-detail-right-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [640, 260, 560, 380]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$cardBg"
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 1
      color: "$border"
  - elementId: p10-detail-right-text
    elementType: text
    bounds: [660, 275, 520, 350]
    content:
      style: "$body"
      fontSize: 15
      lineHeight: 1.6
      align: [left, top]
      text: |
        <p><strong style="color:$primary;">Step 5 重构</strong></p>
        <p>检查代码是否符合 docs/conventions/；提取重复代码，优化命名</p>
        <p style="margin-top:8px"><strong style="color:$primary;">Step 6 Contract Test（API 层）</strong></p>
        <p>为每个新增 Endpoint 编写 Contract；生成 Stub 并验证 API 契约</p>
        <p style="margin-top:8px"><strong style="color:$primary;">Step 7 文档更新</strong></p>
        <p>更新 docs/design/api-spec-v1.md；更新 claude.md 中的 Sprint 状态</p>
        <p style="margin-top:16px"><span style="color:$accent;"><strong>核心原则：红 → 绿 → 重构，循环往复</strong></span></p>
  - elementId: p10-page-num
    elementType: text
    bounds: [1160, 690, 60, 20]
    content:
      style: "$caption"
      align: [right, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: "10"